  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/webkit\/domnode-additions\ncrawled: 2025-12-12T01:25:06Z\n---\n\n# DOMNode Additions\n\n**API Collection**\n\nAdditions to the `DOMNode` class help convert the structured nodes of DOM content into a rich web-viewable form.\n\n## Creating archives\n\n- **webArchive**: A web archive of the content of the node and its children.\n\n## Obtaining layout rectangles\n\n- **boundingBox()**: Returns a rectangle that bounds the onscreen rendering of the node.\n- **lineBoxRects()**: Returns the rectangles that bound each line of text in the node.\n\n## Related Documentation\n\n- **WebKit Objective-C Programming Guide**\n\n## Document Object Model (DOM) APIs\n\n- **DOMAbstractView**\n- **DOMAttr**\n- **DOMBlob**\n- **DOMCDATASection**\n- **DOMCharacterData**\n- **DOMComment**\n- **DOMCounter**\n- **DOMCSSCharsetRule**\n- **DOMCSSFontFaceRule**\n- **DOMCSSImportRule**\n- **DOMCSSMediaRule**\n- **DOMCSSPageRule**\n- **DOMCSSPrimitiveValue**\n- **DOMCSSRule**\n- **DOMCSSRuleList**\n\n",
